                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Primanius Primulus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Augustaliniae Afr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> coniugi dulcissim<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>quae vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXI <expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>ses</ex></expan> IIII dies XXVIII et Lucania <lb n="4"/>Summula mater fili<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> et Augustalinius <lb n="5"/>Afer frater et Primania Primula filia <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 auf dem Deckel, Z. 2-6 auf dem Kasten. Heute offenbar nur noch mehrere nicht mehr aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten.</p>
            </div>
